          <title>Nvidia RTX 5090 GPU: Performance Leaps, But Assassin's Creed Shadows Requirements Suggest Older GPUs May Suffice</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Nvidia's latest RTX 5090 GPU makes notable performance leaps over the previous generation's flagship GPU, with additions such as Multi Frame Generation improving performance using ray tracing at 4K in games. However, Ubisoft's Assassin's Creed Shadows hardware requirements suggest an RTX 4000 series GPU (or older) will suffice.]]></description>
